<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Election Integrity Statements Archive — Brandy Breaks It Down</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Condensed:wght@300;400;700&family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;1,300;1,400&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --ink: #1a1a2e; --parchment: #f5f0e8; --parchment-dark: #e8e0d0;
    --archival-red: #c0392b; --steel-blue: #2e6da4; --muted-gold: #8a6914;
    --verified: #1a6b3c; --disputed: #c0392b; --unverified: #7a6200; --mixed: #5a3e8a;
    --text-main: #1a1a2e; --text-secondary: #4a4a6a; --border: #c8c0b0;
  }
  body { background: var(--parchment); color: var(--text-main); font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; min-height: 100vh; }
  .site-header { background: var(--ink); color: var(--parchment); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--archival-red); }
  .header-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 28px 24px 20px; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .site-brand { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--archival-red); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .site-title { font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--parchment); line-height: 1.2; }
  .header-meta { margin-left: auto; text-align: right; }
  .header-meta p { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #9090b0; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .header-meta strong { color: var(--parchment); }
  .archive-desc { background: #12122a; border-top: 1px solid #2a2a4a; }
  .archive-desc-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 14px 24px; font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #9090b0; line-height: 1.5; }
  .archive-desc-inner em { color: #c0c0d8; font-style: normal; }
  .main-layout { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 28px 24px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr; gap: 28px; align-items: start; }
  .filter-rail { position: sticky; top: 20px; }
  .filter-section { background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 16px; border-radius: 2px; }
  .filter-header { background: var(--ink); color: var(--parchment); font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 8px 14px; }
  .filter-body { padding: 12px 14px; }
  .search-input { width: 100%; padding: 9px 12px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-main); background: var(--parchment); outline: none; transition: border-color 0.15s; }
  .search-input:focus { border-color: var(--steel-blue); }
  .search-input::placeholder { color: #9090a8; }
  .filter-group { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .filter-group label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); cursor: pointer; padding: 3px 0; user-select: none; }
  .filter-group label:hover { color: var(--text-main); }
  .filter-group input[type="checkbox"] { accent-color: var(--steel-blue); width: 14px; height: 14px; cursor: pointer; }
  .party-dot { display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .dot-R { background: #c0392b; } .dot-D { background: #2e6da4; } .dot-I { background: #6a4c93; }
  .status-pip { display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 1px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .pip-verified { background: var(--verified); } .pip-disputed { background: var(--disputed); }
  .pip-mixed { background: var(--mixed); } .pip-unverified { background: var(--unverified); }
  .results-count { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); padding: 10px 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .results-count strong { color: var(--text-main); }
  .clear-btn { width: 100%; padding: 8px; background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-secondary); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .clear-btn:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--parchment); border-color: var(--ink); }
  .cards-toolbar { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
  .sort-label { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .sort-select { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; padding: 5px 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: white; color: var(--text-main); cursor: pointer; border-radius: 2px; }
  .card { background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 4px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 16px; border-radius: 2px; transition: box-shadow 0.15s; overflow: hidden; }
  .card:hover { box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .card.party-R { border-left-color: #c0392b; } .card.party-D { border-left-color: #2e6da4; } .card.party-I { border-left-color: #6a4c93; }
  .card-header { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 16px 10px; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .official-name { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-main); line-height: 1.2; }
  .official-title { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 2px; }
  .card-meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 6px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .date-stamp { font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .status-stamp { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 2px; border: 1.5px solid; }
  .stamp-verified { color: var(--verified); border-color: var(--verified); background: #f0fff4; }
  .stamp-disputed { color: var(--disputed); border-color: var(--disputed); background: #fff5f5; }
  .stamp-mixed { color: var(--mixed); border-color: var(--mixed); background: #f8f4ff; }
  .stamp-unverified { color: var(--unverified); border-color: var(--unverified); background: #fffdf0; }
  .card-quote { padding: 0 16px 12px; font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; color: #2a2a3a; line-height: 1.75; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--parchment-dark); }
  .card-quote::before { content: '\201C'; font-size: 20px; color: var(--border); vertical-align: -3px; margin-right: 3px; }
  .card-quote::after { content: '\201D'; font-size: 20px; color: var(--border); vertical-align: -3px; margin-left: 3px; }
  .card-footer { padding: 10px 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
  .topic-tags { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .tag { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 7px; background: var(--parchment-dark); color: var(--text-secondary); border-radius: 2px; }
  .card-actions { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
  .btn-sm { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 2px; cursor: pointer; border: 1.5px solid; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .btn-source { background: transparent; border-color: var(--border); color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
  .btn-source:hover { border-color: var(--steel-blue); color: var(--steel-blue); }
  .btn-factcheck { background: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink); color: var(--parchment); }
  .btn-factcheck:hover { background: #2c2c50; }
  .btn-factcheck:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }
  .factcheck-panel { display: none; background: #f8f4ff; border-top: 2px solid var(--mixed); padding: 16px; font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-main); }
  .factcheck-panel.open { display: block; }
  .factcheck-panel.loading { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: var(--text-secondary); font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; }
  .factcheck-header { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mixed); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .factcheck-content p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .factcheck-content p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .factcheck-sources { margin-top: 12px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #d0c8e8; font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .spinner { width: 18px; height: 18px; border: 2px solid var(--border); border-top-color: var(--mixed); border-radius: 50%; animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite; flex-shrink: 0; }
  @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
  .empty-state { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; color: var(--text-secondary); font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; }
  .empty-state .empty-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .empty-state h3 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text-main); }
  .methodology { background: #12122a; color: #9090b0; padding: 20px 24px; font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .methodology-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .methodology strong { color: #c0c0d8; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .main-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .filter-rail { position: static; } .header-meta { display: none; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="site-brand">Brandy Breaks It Down · Research Archive</div>
      <h1 class="site-title">Election Integrity Statements<br>Public Record</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <p>Updated <strong id="init-date"></strong></p>
      <p>Sources: Congressional Record, C-SPAN, Official Press Releases, AP, NPR, PolitiFact</p>
      <p>Primary sources only · No partisan interpretation</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="archive-desc">
    <div class="archive-desc-inner">
      A chronological record of verified public statements by elected officials on mail voting, voter registration, turnout, and election integrity.
      <em>All quotes are from primary or contemporaneously documented sources. Fact-check analysis is AI-assisted and cites empirical evidence.</em>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="main-layout">
  <aside class="filter-rail">
    <div class="filter-section">
      <div class="filter-header">Search Statements</div>
      <div class="filter-body"><input type="text" class="search-input" id="search-input" placeholder="keyword, official, topic…"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-section">
      <div class="filter-header">Party</div>
      <div class="filter-body">
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-party" value="R" checked><span class="party-dot dot-R"></span>Republican</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-party" value="D" checked><span class="party-dot dot-D"></span>Democrat</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-party" value="I" checked><span class="party-dot dot-I"></span>Independent</label></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-section">
      <div class="filter-header">Topic</div>
      <div class="filter-body">
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-topic" value="mail-voting" checked>Mail Voting</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-topic" value="voter-id" checked>Voter ID / DPOC</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-topic" value="noncitizen" checked>Non-Citizen Voting</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-topic" value="turnout" checked>Turnout / Registration</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-topic" value="integrity" checked>Election Integrity</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-topic" value="fraud" checked>Fraud Claims</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-topic" value="save-act" checked>SAVE Act / DPOC Law</label></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-section">
      <div class="filter-header">Evidentiary Status</div>
      <div class="filter-body">
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-status" value="verified" checked><span class="status-pip pip-verified"></span>Verified / Accurate</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-status" value="mixed" checked><span class="status-pip pip-mixed"></span>Partially Accurate</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-status" value="disputed" checked><span class="status-pip pip-disputed"></span>Disputed / Inaccurate</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-status" value="unverified" checked><span class="status-pip pip-unverified"></span>Unverified / Contested</label></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-section">
      <div class="filter-header">Year</div>
      <div class="filter-body">
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-year" value="2018" checked>2018</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-year" value="2020" checked>2020</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-year" value="2021" checked>2021</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-year" value="2022" checked>2022</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-year" value="2023" checked>2023</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-year" value="2024" checked>2024</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-year" value="2025" checked>2025</label></div>
        <div class="filter-group"><label><input type="checkbox" class="filter-year" value="2026" checked>2026</label></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-section">
      <div class="results-count"><strong id="result-count">—</strong> statements shown</div>
      <div class="filter-body"><button class="clear-btn" id="clear-filters">Reset All Filters</button></div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <main class="cards-area">
    <div class="cards-toolbar">
      <span class="sort-label">Sort by:</span>
      <select class="sort-select" id="sort-select">
        <option value="date-desc">Date (newest first)</option>
        <option value="date-asc">Date (oldest first)</option>
        <option value="name">Official (A–Z)</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div id="cards-container"></div>
  </main>
</div>

<footer class="methodology">
  <div class="methodology-inner">
    <strong>Methodology:</strong> Statements are drawn from primary sources only: congressional transcripts, C-SPAN, official press releases, White House records, and contemporaneously documented news transcripts with verifiable audio/video.
    Evidentiary status reflects peer-reviewed research, government audit findings, and nonpartisan fact-checker consensus (PolitiFact, AP Fact Check, FactCheck.org).
    <strong>Note on mail voting:</strong> Academic evidence consistently finds that mail voting modestly increases turnout but does not produce a durable partisan advantage for either party. Claims to the contrary are marked accordingly.
    <strong>Note on noncitizen voting:</strong> Documented instances are vanishingly rare. Utah's 2025 statewide audit of 2 million voters found one confirmed noncitizen registration and zero confirmed noncitizen votes. A Brennan Center survey of 44 jurisdictions after 2016 found roughly 30 noncitizen ballots among 23.5 million votes cast (0.0001%).
    · <strong>AI Fact-Check</strong> uses Claude claude-sonnet-4-6; responses are a research aid, not legal or journalistic determination. Always verify primary sources independently.
  </div>
</footer>

